text: "He Said She Said" is a 2021 song by the Scottish synth-pop band Chvrches. It is the first single from their third studio album Screen Violence which was released in 2021. ==Charts== Weekly chart performance for "He Said She Said" Chart (2021) Peak position ==References== Category:2021 songs Category:Chvrches songs
